values:
i love bret michaels.
i don't have big enough boobs though. 
k haha.
i just want to be on vh1.

hi. 

i've been reading through my friends livejournals. cheer up people, move on and get happy. g-g-g-get happy. i'm serious, it's so pointless being sad for so long. go out and do something. met new people, walk through the park, cook, draw on the side walk with chalk, blow bubbles, make your life worth living. sitting in front of a computer confusing how upset you are to the internet is a lifeless life. 

i just want my friends, and maybe not so close friends, to be happy. i really care about you all. i'm not around a lot, i know this, but just know i always have your back.

stephanie, i have been sticking up for you 100%. you have no idea how many arguements i have been in with my brother for you. i stuck up for you in the worse situation, you may not know it, but i did. i love you, honey. 

ashley, i don't know if you even use lj anymore, but i miss you! you have no clue how much i miss our shopping trips and how much i miss how we like the same style in clothes and actually understand whats ugly and whats hot. 

tara, i know you don't use lj. so forget about it. i remembered you though.




OKAY.
ANYWAY.

i have a sleeping problem. all in all, it's pretty tight. 
i don't sleep. i don't get tired. i have so much energy. 
seriously, i can't even force myself to sleep. 
kind of weird, but i like it. 
it maybe because i have changed my lifesyle. 
i am now vegan.
i don't party anymore, and if i am at a party i don't drink but maybe one beer. 
i feel so healthy. 
i don't know whats up.
: )


OKAY.
ALSO.
 
i know what love is, i am in love. 

OKAY.
AND.

i am going on a trip with mark (my bf) and his family July 14 and i will be gone a week. we are going to a secluded island. fancy-smancy. i am pretty pumped about this trip. it will be a lot of fun.

OKAY.
BYE.

i hate myspace. reason why: i hate stumbling on to pictures of the boy i like kissing a girl. not that the picture is recent, but that its him being involved with another girl. in conclusion: fuck you, myspace! and fuck me being bored and me lurking.

hi ya. drug tests are dumb. i mean, i could understand why you would need one to, lets say, operate a bus full of children. to work at a music store though? that's just not right! now don't get me wrong, i'm not a stoner, i just don't want to take the time to take the test. i mean, i may have smoked a couple days ago, but thats not my life. so, basically, i am going to fail this drug test. anyway, other than that, my interview today went well. if i get this job, i think i may be done with pot. believe it or not...? tonight i am going over to my grandmom's house for a retirement party for one of my relatives! oh the fun and excited i shall have! then after that, mark will get off work much later... but i'm hanging out with him later. possibly. i mean, i may be just worn the fuck out after partying with the relatives. ha, i'm kidding. i don't stop partying. BYE K

has anyones valentines day actually been good?

i mean i got dumped right before valentines day and i am still living with that person.

valentines day makes me very sad.
tattoo this saturday. who wants to go with me? i am getting a rocket ship, but it will be 928374982165x better than that because someone amazing is doing it.

february is not my favorite month.
although it is my birthay month, i hate february.
its so damn cold, and i'm always sick during this month. 
valentines day blows, not just because i'm in an awful relationship or no relationship at all, it blows because even if i am in a rleationship during this holiday i am always in the worst moods. i hate that day, february 14th.
it's a short month, which means rent is due earlier!
my birthday , february 23rd, isn't so bad.
i'll be 19 this year and hopefully i'll get my head on straight and run away from this hell-hole.

oh also, world of warcraft has taken over my life. 
i dream about it. 
i think about it before i go to sleep. at work. while i'm cleaning. while i'm cooking. while i'm playing other games. 
when i play it, i can't get off of it easily. 

yes, world of warcraft, i think you're my true love.

tattoos soon, in about two weeks. anyone want to come with me?
i think i am going to get the horde logo or 'FOR THE HORDE' tattoo'd across my ass cheeks.

haha.
:)

that means i am putting my two weeks notice in at hot topic today. 
i am kind of sad about leaving my friends there, but i will visit them i am sure. 
i am glad to be leaving though. 

bye.

i just wake up way too late for work and then get home from work exhausted. 
tonight, i am showering.


oh, and i hope ACS calls me today. 
i am absolutely sick of working at the mall.
YEAH, I KNOW.

i need a shower. 
that basically sums up my life right now. 
oh and i haven't changed clothes in 2 days.
hot shit.

suger free chocolate pudding and diet mountain dew, that was my breakfast and lunch. 
i have a feeling that is all i will be eating today considering i have no money, at all. 
actually, i lied. i have about 3 dollars in quarters. yesterday i had to buy my cigarettes with dimes and nickels. oh well.

party tonight. after work, i have a feeling when i get to the party though, my boy and his friends will aleady be drunk and nearly passed out. i will just have to catch up fast. don't plan on getting ahold of me tonight, i will be wasted by midnight. 

i work tomorrow at 3. i really wish i still lived in lexington. the commute from richmond to lexington everyday is getting longer and a little more boring each day.

well, i'm off. bye.

Things I would like to do before Christmas, well one thing I would like to do before Christmas is to go to a Holiday Concert at a Middle School or Elementary School. 
I think that would be really creepy for me to do, but I really would like to go. 

I WANT SNOW!
I can't wait to look out my window when I wake up and see snow. 
I don't even mind that i have to drive from Richmond to Lexington everyday, even though snow can be mega dangerous. 

I'm finally at the point where I really don't care about relationships with boys. I don't need a man to make me happy, shheeeit. 
Although, when I do find a guy that I like then that's fine as long as he won't hurt me. 

TUUURRRRRTTTLLLEEEEE POOOWWWWEERRRR!
:\

i need to keep telling myself that 'i don't need a boy to be happy'.
but you know, i really really like and care about someone, but they like someone else now and they are happy. 
and i've seriously tried to move on from my mistake, but it has been so difficult to try to leave something so important to me. 
and i know that they have no idea how much i care about them, and even if they did know, i'm not 100% if they would care. 
i think it's love, but i'm pretty sure there is no hope.
i'm a negative girl.

BENGE IS HEARTS: when you're with me we will live off wine.

working 8 hours at hot topic two days straight isn't a healthy lifestyle.
and then tomorrow i work 8 hours again and then monday i work 7 and a half hours. 
i'm making money though, so i will be a'okay. 

i have tuesday off and thursday off. that's all. 
make plans with me on monday night. 
i'm thinking a lot of alcohol and some OUT OF CONTROL break dancing.

Portugal the Man show fell through, I knew in the back of my mind that it would. I need to learn from this situation that I am facing and get away from it. I have been so upset because of a boy, a boy, i never ever do that.

I am really thankful to have Brian there for me. 

My body really hurts, on the right side of my belly. Whats on that side of my body? I seriously have no idea, I just know it hurts.

My New Years Resolution: To be happy and to not let people get me down.

i got kicked out of my house in lexington this morning around 9am. 
yesterday was awful, and my dad made sure that my day started off awful this morning as well.

i am living in richmond now, i guess.
i mean, i don't mind it at all.
but traveling back and forth to lexington is rough.

:\ oh well.


"We're going to a party, it's a birthday party. It's your birthday party, happy birthday darling. We love you very, very, very, very, very, very, very much."

tomorrow will be much better than today, so i am hoping.

fucking stupid. 
yeah, really.
